rows.label: tlk70000001_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Gargoyle attack is worst thing
ever happen to shopping ward.
Everyone in complete shock!

rows.label: tlk70000001_02_msg0002
rows.name:
But no use just standing around
with mouth agape. Unless shops
open, trade completely doomed!

rows.label: tlk70000001_02_msg0003
rows.name: That where Chamber of Commerce come in!

rows.label: tlk70000001_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Clean up, repairs, distribution
of food... Biggipon, littlepon,
all pitch in! Everyone work hard.

rows.label: tlk70000001_02_msg0006
rows.name:
Morumo was pitching in too.
Could not have people thinking
chairman not pull own weight!

rows.label: tlk70000001_02_msg0007
rows.name:
All hard work put market back
on feet in record time!

rows.label: tlk70000001_02_msg0008
rows.name:
Everyone work really, really hard!
Morumo still mighty impressed...
